      "id": "PopularPost77469",
      "post_content": "At worst it is a 1/1 for two.  \nOn closer inspection, its first ability can give you a 3/3 blocker at the least if you've a spare create.  \nAnd its last ability is essentially a reusable Essence Shatter! Even sacrificing itself you have a creature-counterspell for turn 3 or one late game for 2UUB.",
